rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0003
rows.name:
Right now, I just want to get
to Aletta and meet up with the
resistance as soon as I can.

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0005
rows.name:
Let's take the ferry from Lasqam
Harbor to get to Aletta.

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0006
rows.name:
Instead of some plain old
regular boat, why can't we
take the Emperor's fancy one?

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0007
rows.name:
I'm not going to say it
again. We can't have a
warship entering Iira...

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0010
rows.name:
Hehe... I'm just so happy that
Kagutsuchi has made a new friend.

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0011
rows.name:
Your Majesty... it's
not like that at all.
